  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Twin Rooms </strong>are between 16-20m² and sleep two people. Superior Twin Rooms with a balcony are available for a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms </strong>are between 18-22m² and sleep up to three people. They have a balcony. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suite </strong>are between 38-44m² and sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed). They have a lounge or seating area and come with bathrobes and slippers.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Double Rooms for sole use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local Fees &amp; Taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of approx. €1.40 per person per night is payable locally</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
